    "In the structural network, the relationship between nodes is determined according to the citation relationship between different documents.",
    "SDBLP is a simplified dataset of DBLP, in which nodes with less than 3 references are deleted, it is that nodes with node degree less than 3 will be deleted.",
    "This paper compares D2GCN with the following baseline methods designed to generate node embedding: DeepGCNs (structure): this model inputs the structural features to Current DeepGCNs.",
